legacy.full_text: Finally, the long-expected China aided Training Seminar on Beef Cattle Feeding and Training Seminar on Chick & Parent Stock Hatchery have been successfully opened this morning at Maseru Avani,  from which 90 Basotho participants will benefit. result.text: Lesotho is a landlocked country enclaved within South Africa. Situated in the Maluti Mountains, the entire country is about 1,000 meters above sea level and is home to one of the few ski resorts on the continent.
